---
description: UI pattern for Accessibility
alwaysApply: true
---

- Approach:  
  - Use semantic Compose APIs (e.g. AccessibleRole)  
  - Ensure focus order and content descriptions are set  
  - Test with TalkBack and high-contrast display modes

- Requirements:
  - Follow Material Design accessibility guidelines
  - Support screen readers
  - Consider color contrast
  - Provide alternative interaction methods
